Brief installation instructions.
R-scape
http://selab.org
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Starting from a source distribution, R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@.tar.gz:
 uncompress:                uncompress R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@.tar.gz  
 unpack:                    tar xf R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@.tar
 move into new directory:   cd R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@
 configure:                 ./configure
 build:                     make
 environmental variable:    RSCAPEDIR set to path-to-directory R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@



For complete documentation, see the R-scape User's Guide (Userguide.pdf).

The default installation produces executable: R-scape_@RSCAPE_VERSION@/src/R-scape

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
